{
  "stem": "11174.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I went in there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And all I saw was a lot of valises packed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were quite a few people there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Here and there, a woman went back and forth.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember that there were a few passports laid out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My passport, he signed in my hand, holding it in my hand, he signed it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Put the stamp--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sugihara, , a Japanese man, you know, a Japanese consulate.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He signed it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And later, we still didn't believe.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The fact was that some people applied with this, applied to the Russian NKVD-- they were the bosses over it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It wasn't supposed to be there, but they were the bosses over it, to apply for exit visa.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then started rumors that they're going to-- they did it for a trick, because historically since the Bolsheviks came to power, they were hardly ever allowed people to get out.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Only in few individual cases.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So there was rumors that they're going to send everybody to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Some people who had a lot of money, a few people, one from Czechoslovakia, paid a lot of money to get out the passports from there, because they were afraid they would send to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Of course, then when people started to go, two people committed suicide, because they got so heart-broken that they couldn't-- that they took out those papers they give them.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But that was it and then we went over to Japan.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You go-- what?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Japan?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then all of a sudden, first you had to put an application to these Russian authorities to get out.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And every day was a list whose papers were already signed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I waited.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My papers came quite late.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was a little nervous.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it came, exit visa.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
